column1: #Text=Shiro Shinobi says : " Looks like the Fire Ferrets have ferreted out a last minute replacement waterbender .
#Text=Just try not to get knocked off the ring .
#Text=" Korra says : " You got it , captain .
#Text=" Referee says : " Fire Ferret waterbender , penalty !
#Text=" Mako says : " You 're only allowed to knock players off the back of the ring !
#Text=" Shiro Shinobi says : " And we 're back in action after that hiccup , but I 'm not so sure this replacement player knows what she 's doing .
#Text=" Shiro Shinobi says : " The Platypus Bears take round one !
#Text=The Platypus Bears know a green player when they see one , and they are focusing the brunt of their bending on this poor girl !
#Text=" Shiro Shinobi says : " Wait a minute !
#Text=" Shiro Shinobi says : " Did I see that right ?
#Text=Hold on , folks , we 're just waiting for the referee 's official call , but ... I - I think this replacement player could be ... no , there 's no way !
#Text=" Tenzin says : " Pardon me , everyone , have you seen Korra this evening ?
#Text=" Shiro Shinobi says : " You 've got ta be kidding me !
#Text=" Tenzin says : " I 'll get her myself !
#Text=" Referee says : " The Avatar will be permitted to continue so long as she solely bends water !
